 class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94be123b515224137b96397900d0707da2dafc06","tid":2484790,"uid":59818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T14:38:05.000Z","msg":"一千蚊夠拍幾集臥底旅行團<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bb9a117956d1e205aeff608dedea455292d3cc6","tid":2484790,"uid":121471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T14:47:30.000Z","msg":"星期二三同一個幸運員俾左一次500<br />\n結果星期四有兩個俾足1000<br />\n補返數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0a6fc83a706aa9c374d9c8408d471b51cf8304f","tid":2484790,"uid":122891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T14:57:48.000Z","msg":"佢兩個9upper 真係好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd6860e969caa0c224e1bfae5e27791ac741d243","tid":2484790,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T15:01:47.000Z","msg":"個師傅整拉絲都幾核突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bebdd5592ed07a484289a1a7a680c80e16b7526d","tid":2484790,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2bb9a117956d1e205aeff608dedea455292d3cc6","tid":2484790,"uid":121471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T14:47:30.000Z","msg":"星期二三同一個幸運員俾左一次500<br />\n結果星期四有兩個俾足1000<br />\n補返數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T15:02:13.000Z","msg":"爽皮<br />\n廢事佢地打交"},{"pid":"c32101046e3fd22003886aebfe24411b4dd1d760","tid":2484790,"uid":81782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T21:33:55.000Z","msg":"間上門海膽之前藍扮黃俾人踢爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<blockquote>呢間<strong><span class=\"gold\">S2鐵皮燒上年因為8月5日「休市」、唔再落TVB廣告而被列為黃店</span></strong>，所以舊TVB團隊出過「爆買支持」任務，於是乎<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">S2鐵板燒就拎住舊團隊張文宣cap水，生意做得盆滿缽滿</span></span></strong>！<br />\n<br />\n但最近「終極黃藍地圖」就踢爆，<strong><span class=\"red\">原來佢哋上年85係無休市架，樂師傅暗地裡仲要鬧員工放假去發夢、密謀打入中国市場</span></strong>，我哋豈能讓呢啲「黃皮藍心」嘅鋪頭繼續「呃」手足嘅錢？證據如下：<br />\n<br />\n[quote]<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUYLYRQQGcLLw3J56Sp6C69yjBXju6zwJNWHYpSa66RK6?filename=m88HegP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm88HegP.jpg&h=17a71d27&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbL2XdbFeb39Pxw9VzzQanKqSwZkV3g3dqYR5sEQ71KAP?filename=1Css9FF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1Css9FF.jpg&h=81a8939c&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmatTZsNWiVr98RJnRtAETaUkc43QfvasHzhZmjsG9b3ka?filename=0aMQ7tU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0aMQ7tU.jpg&h=0057b177&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n親中商會過黎食飯，老闆樂師傅會要求所有員工要在身上貼上國旗，佢自己亦有貼國旗係身(中)；<br />\n樂師傅被人質疑係藍店既時候，曾經用sayno2tvb團隊既「爆買圖」幫自己「澄清」(右) </p></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\"><strong>表明不希望在蘋果動出現，只因希望打入大陸市場</strong></span></span><br />\n「唔想響蘋果動見到我間餐廳話&hellip;我個名休息呀我同你講，我點打入大陸市場呀吓？我搞咁多嘢都係為咗想打入大陸市場咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\"><strong>「12/8 和你飛」後責罵員工放假入機場</strong></span></span><br />\n「平時喺公司你地講政治我已經唔理你地嫁啦知唔知呀，唔係關於你入機場問題呀，係今日爆呀明唔明白呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://lih.kg/2161346\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2161346</a>"},{"pid":"e6e086cf7daf49f94a17c8db1f469557d2d1e9e3","tid":2484790,"uid":364850,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"36b1e4a3cb6ec9c6cad9d4c06c9e1c4b55f37a19","tid":2484790,"uid":148355,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"de5b4c50999d9c919810523a85c0cff546ddf7b6","tid":2484790,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"8d6d799ae9dd3df5d38144554f77bf13035da12a","tid":2484790,"uid":148355,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy